      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape, ready for many more adventures. It drives super smoothly and has been really well-loved over the years. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make the next owner very happy. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
