    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, sending power through the factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity, and the rod bearings have been addressed. The suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and a set of Bilstein dampers, providing excellent turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains in peak synchronization, offering the pure analog feedback this chassis is heralded for.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
