    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of dependability and comfort. Under the hood, the engine performs flawlessly with a consistent idle and responsive acceleration, complemented by a transmission that shifts through every gear with precision. The interior has been meticulously cared for; the seating surfaces are supple and clean, and every feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates as intended. While the exterior displays a deep, glossy finish, it shows the light, honest character of a well-loved car, including minor road nicks and faint surface marks that do not detract from its overall curb appeal. It has recently undergone a full professional detailing and a comprehensive mechanical check-up, making it a turn-key option for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality ride.",
      "price": 34800.0,
